  "phases": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "case_id": 37,
      "phase_number": 1,
      "phase_name": "户型分析",
      "layout_images": "[\"/upload/cases/layout_37_1.jpg\"]",
      "layout_analysis": "<p>原始户型为三室两厅一卫，户型方正，采光良好。主要问题：1. 入户无玄关，隐私性差；2. 厨房封闭式，与餐厅互动性弱；3. 收纳空间不足。</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "case_id": 37,
      "phase_number": 2,
      "phase_name": "设计意境",
      "mood_images": "[\"/upload/cases/mood_37_1.jpg\", \"/upload/cases/mood_37_2.jpg\"]",
      "mood_text": "<p>客户偏好现代简约风格，追求干净利落的空间感。色调以白色、浅灰为主，局部点缀木色和莫兰迪色系，营造温馨舒适的居家氛围。</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "case_id": 37,
      "phase_number": 3,
      "phase_name": "平面规划",
      "plan_image": "/upload/cases/plan_37.jpg",
      "plan_text": "<p>优化方案：1. 入户增设玄关鞋柜，提升隐私性；2. 厨房改为开放式+岛台设计，增强空间互动；3. 全屋定制收纳系统，储物空间提升40%；4. 主卧增设衣帽间，提升居住品质。</p>"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "case_id": 37,
      "phase_number": 4,
      "phase_name": "鸟瞰展示",
      "birdview_images": "[\"/upload/cases/birdview_37_1.jpg\", \"/upload/cases/birdview_37_2.jpg\"]"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "case_id": 37,
      "phase_number": 5,
      "phase_name": "效果图首页",
      "showcase_images": "[\"/upload/cases/render_37_1.jpg\", \"/upload/cases/render_37_2.jpg\", \"/upload/cases/render_37_3.jpg\"]",
      "showcase_title1": "现代简约",
      "showcase_title2": "高新誉峰三室两厅全案设计",
      "showcase_text_cn": "<p>本案位于成都高新区誉峰小区，面积180㎡，三室两厅户型。设计核心：开放式厨房+岛台，增强家人互动；全屋定制收纳系统，储物空间提升40%；现代简约风格，白色+浅灰主色调，局部木色点缀。</p>",
      "showcase_text_en": "<p>This case is located in Yufeng Community, High-tech Zone, Chengdu, with an area of 180㎡ and a three-bedroom two-living-room layout. Design core: Open kitchen + island to enhance family interaction; Whole-house custom storage system, storage space increased by 40%; Modern minimalist style, white + light gray main color, partial wood color embellishment.</p>"
    },
